unittitle_ssm: Account book for construction of buildings on Pineapple Street, Brooklyn
abstract_ssm: One account book, kept by an unnamed construction company, relating to the construction of buildings at #60 and #62 Pineapple Street in Brooklyn during the period 1884 to 1886.  The book details estimates and transactions in accounts held with various sub-contractors and suppliers.  An index of company names is included.
